description: This is a simple skill to tell you the current Polls-plus forecast from http://projects.fivethirtyeight.com/2016-election-forecast/#plus for the US Presidential Election. The odds are checked every 10 minutes.
exampleInteractions: Alexa, ask election odds who is winning?
Alexa, ask election odds will Hillary win?
Alexa, ask election odds what's the story?
name: Election Odds
shortDescription: Simple skill to tell you the current Polls-plus forecast from 538 for the US Presidential Election.
